SidebarDesktopContent/HTTPAPIRequired: Firstly, Open TidGi-desktop's HTTP API feature on current workspace's setting, see [[Official TidGi Feature Handbook|https://tidgi.fun/#TidGi%20Feature%20Handbook%2FEnabling%20HTTP%20API]] for details.
