SidebarDesktopContent/ConnectedClients: Connected clients
SidebarDesktopContent/ViewConnectedClients: Click to view connected clients

SidebarMobileContent/SyncWithDesktop: Sync With Desktop
SidebarMobileContent/UseWikiList: Use TidGi-Mobile's wiki list to sync (long press wiki item in the list to open menu)
SidebarMobileContent/ServerList: Server List

Readme/Title: Sync Between TidGi Desktop and TidGi-Mobile
Readme/Intro: This plugin provides Git Smart HTTP sync endpoints for TidGi-Mobile to sync with TidGi Desktop workspaces via `isomorphic-git`.
Readme/Diagram: TidGi-Mobile App ↔ Desktop App ↔ Cloud
Readme/TiddloidNote: Tiddloid is not supported. Use the `tw-html-nodejs-sync` plugin instead.
Readme/HowToUse/Title: How to use
Readme/HowToUse/Step1: Enable HTTP API on the current workspace in TidGi Desktop (see [[Official TidGi Feature Handbook|https://tidgi.fun/#TidGi%20Feature%20Handbook%2FEnabling%20HTTP%20API]])
Readme/HowToUse/Step2: Open the MobileSync sidebar tab and scan the Git sync QR code with TidGi-Mobile
Readme/HowToUse/Step3: Manage sync from TidGi-Mobile's wiki list (long press a wiki item to open the menu)
Readme/ConnectedClients/Title: Connected clients
Readme/ConnectedClients/Body: After clicking "View connected clients" in the desktop sidebar, recently connected mobile clients and their latest sync summary are shown.
Readme/Requirements/Title: Requirements
Readme/Requirements/Body: Needs official QR plugin [[$:/plugins/tiddlywiki/qrcode]] for QR codes in the sidebar.
